OL,7,FA fraudster who posed as a builder and
OL,8,Fconned multiple elderly people out of
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds in Gloucester has
OL,10,Fbeen sentenced.
OL,12,FDean Croucher stole around #10,000
OL,13,Ffrom vulnerable victims and admitted
OL,14,Fdefrauding two elderly people between
OL,15,FFebruary 2021 and December 2023.
OL,17,FThe 35-year-old pleaded guilty to four
OL,18,Fcounts of fraud and two counts of
OL,19,Ftheft at Gloucester Crown Court on
OL,20,FFriday 14 June.
