OL,7,FThe judge sentenced Croucher to pay
OL,8,F#1,800 in compensation to his victims
OL,9,Fand to complete 200 hours of unpaid
OL,10,Fwork, at Gloucester Crown Court on 23
OL,11,FJuly.
OL,13,FHe was also given two restraining
OL,14,Forders and two community orders.
