OL,7,FSergeant Tom Francis, from the
OL,8,FGloucester Neighbourhood Policing
OL,9,FTeam, said: "Historically, these
OL,10,Foffences can be difficult to detect
OL,11,Fowing to the vulnerabilities of the
OL,12,Fvictims involved and the calculating
OL,13,Fnature of those responsible for such
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,16,F"Thanks to the dedication of PC Luke
OL,17,FSavigar-Jones, who has invested
OL,18,Fhundreds of hours into collecting
OL,19,Fevidence as well as safeguarding one
OL,20,Fof Croucher's victims, we were able to
OL,21,Fbring this case to court.
