OL,7,F"I would also like to praise the
OL,8,Fvictims for coming forward and
OL,9,Freporting the incidents to us in the
OL,10,Ffirst place.
OL,12,F"Sometimes victims of rogue traders
OL,13,Fmay not be aware that they are being
OL,14,Fdefrauded so I would urge anyone who
OL,15,Fis concerned about an elderly or
OL,16,Fvulnerable friend or relative to
OL,17,Freport it to police".
